---
import ChapterShell from "../../../components/ChapterShell.astro";
import Section from "../../../components/Section.astro";
import DiagramFigure from "../../../components/diagrams/DiagramFigure.astro";
import CompactionProjectionKeystone from "../../../components/diagrams/CompactionProjectionKeystone.astro";
import CompactKindsFlow from "../../../components/diagrams/CompactKindsFlow.astro";
import HighWaterCompactFlow from "../../../components/diagrams/HighWaterCompactFlow.astro";
---

<ChapterShell chapterId="03" locale="en">
  <div slot="thesis">
    <p lang="zh-CN">
      （正文仍以中文源稿为准）上下文窗口会满；Compaction 让模型合法地忘记旧轮次，同时历史事实仍可从
      log / 证据层找回——忘记的是投影，不是世界。
    </p>
    <p>
      Structural parity with the zh draft: scene → keystone → three layers → high water → rolling →
      three compact kinds → failure → not-what. Full EN prose is not same-ship yet — chapter remains
      WIP.
    </p>
  </div>

  <Section
    id="keystone"
    label="§03 · Keystone"
    title="Compaction projects the log"
    lede="Scene-local metaphor; fixed system is NewsLiquid tokens, hand keystones, and motion discipline."
  >
    <DiagramFigure
      prototype
      caption="Fig. 1 · Canonical log → durable checkpoint → ephemeral provider request; source log remains replayable."
      alt="Runtime Events Log fans into HistoryCompactCheckpoint and recent raw Events tail; Materialize feeds a dashed Provider request; invariant: Compaction projects the log and never mutates canonical RuntimeEvents."
    >
      <CompactionProjectionKeystone />
    </DiagramFigure>
  </Section>

  <Section
    id="high-water"
    label="§03 · Trigger"
    title="High water → fold → durable → replay"
    lede="EN captions only; narrative body lives in the zh chapter until bilingual same-ship."
  >
    <DiagramFigure
      caption="Fig. 2 · LLM produces summary value; Runtime owns coverage, durability, and replay gates."
      alt="Five-step flow: Past high water, LLM summary, Durable append, Coverage gate, Replay with raw tail."
    >
      <HighWaterCompactFlow />
    </DiagramFigure>
    <aside class="history-aside">
      <p class="history-aside__tag">Evolution aside</p>
      <p>
        Architecture chapter land:
        <a href="/history/pr/772">maka:pr:772</a>.
      </p>
    </aside>
  </Section>

  <Section
    id="kinds"
    label="§03 · Boundaries"
    title="Three compacts, not one feature"
    lede="History LLM compaction ≠ active prune ≠ semanticCompact."
  >
    <DiagramFigure
      caption="Fig. 3 · Same direction (do not mutate source), different durability contracts."
      alt="Three columns comparing History LLM compaction, Active Tool Result Prune, and semanticCompact."
    >
      <CompactKindsFlow />
    </DiagramFigure>
  </Section>

  <div slot="outline">
    <ul class="outline-list">
      <li>Structure + figures mirrored from zh; full EN prose pending</li>
      <li>
        Aside target: <a href="/history/pr/772">maka:pr:772</a>
      </li>
      <li>Do not mark checklist complete</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</ChapterShell>

<style>
  .outline-list {
    margin: 0.75rem 0 0;
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
    max-width: 40em;
  }

  .outline-list li {
    margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
  }
</style>
